name: Music City - Love Journey
description:
Have you ever lived in a music city? Where you can show everyone your gift in rap. Falling in fantastic music. Dance with cg5. Friday night is coming. Are you ready?
Try your best to beat your enemies by using right arrows up, down, left, and right at every funkin mission place. Keep up that good work to the end!
Enjoy this music city!
Keep up your own love journey!
Have fun!
